### Test Checkout Flow

### Login
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

### Get Cart (requires token from login response)
GET http://localhost:3001/cart
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Add to Cart
POST http://localhost:3001/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "souvenir_id": "SOUVENIR_ID_HERE",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Checkout - Create Order
POST http://localhost:3001/payment/orders
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "VNPAY"
}

### Get Order
GET http://localhost:3001/payment/orders
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

